---
description: "Logging configuration and file management rules"
type: agent-select
globs:
  - "**/*.py"
  - "**/*.sh"
  - "**/*.yml"
  - "**/*.yaml"
  - "**/*.log"
alwaysApply: false
---
- **All log files must be created in the `logs/` directory** at the project root.
- Use structured logging with appropriate log levels (DEBUG, INFO, WARNING, ERROR).
- Use descriptive log file names (e.g., `rag_system.log`, `cli.log`).
